title: 'Mademoiselle Zhivago' Movie [2013] WEBRip (Lara Fabian)
description:
Starring: Lara Fabian
Production Date: 2011
Web Release Date: 2013  (Russia/Ukraine)
Director: Alan Badoev
Country: Ukraine
Language: French

Length: 51 mins
Format: MP4 | 720p

Plot:
The final version of Mademoiselle Zhivago consists in 8 short stories, representing songs from the album that has the same name. The original project is not only musical, but also cinematographic. In theory it should tell the story of a woman who crosses different lives over the years and centuries, although the final cut was edited per request of Lara Fabian herself, destroying the original time-sequence of the movie, and transforming it into a series of videoclips.

Enjoy!
